# CDXC:PublicRelease 2026-04-27-05:36: Keep generated Storybook output,
# native build products, and runtime logs out of the public repository while
# preserving each developer's local copies.
# CDXC:AgentInstructions 2026-06-13-09:26: Track the repo AGENTS.md so Ghostex
# native layout and hit-testing requirements travel with app source instead of
# living only as a local ignored instruction file. Keep private agent skill
# folders ignored separately.
# CDXC:Distribution 2026-04-28-04:19: Release DMG/ZIP artifacts are uploaded to
# GitHub Releases and referenced by Homebrew casks, so git should track source
# and metadata only instead of committing binary distribution outputs.
# CDXC:Distribution 2026-05-27-10:11: Android APK downloads are also release
# artifacts. Keep local APK copies out of source commits for the same reason as
# macOS DMGs and ZIPs.
# CDXC:Distribution 2026-06-04-01:42: Local Android APK artifacts moved under
# release/downloads so release outputs are grouped together while the old
# downloads/*.apk ignore remains as a guard for stale local scripts.
# CDXC:CliInstall 2026-06-07-13:53: The macOS build stages app-bundled CLI launchers under native/macos/ghostexHost/CLI before Xcode copies them into Contents/Resources/CLI. Keep that folder ignored like Web because it is generated from scripts/ghostex-cli.mjs, scripts/ghostex-cli-launcher.sh, and scripts/skills.
# CDXC:RepoSafety 2026-05-27-10:44: Image-generation scratch outputs under
# tmp/imagegen are intermediate asset experiments, not source assets. Commit
# only the selected asset destination so releases stay source-only and
# reproducible.
# CDXC:RepoSafety 2026-05-02-00:11: The ghostex release-to-brew skill is local
# agent workflow documentation and must remain available on this machine without
# appearing in the public GitHub repository tree.
# CDXC:RepoSafety 2026-05-10-10:21: Fresh workspace state records local window
# layout for this developer machine and should not be published with ghostex source
# or release metadata.
# CDXC:RepoSafety 2026-05-15-15:03: The pre-rename zmuxHost Web bundle path can
# still receive generated sidebar assets from stale local tooling. Keep it
# ignored like the current ghostexHost Web directory so generated JS/CSS bundles
# never enter release commits.
.idea
react-doctor.config.json
.ignore
.ignored/

# CDXC:ReleaseDocs 2026-05-12-13:09: Local planning notes that should not be
# published with product docs live under `.ignored/` instead of needing
# per-file ignore rules.
.tmp-*
